---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于" description="关于蘇里：个人简介与联系方式。">
  <article class="prose about">
    <img class="avatar" src="/Y.png" width="112" height="112" alt="蘇里的头像" />
    <h1>关于</h1>
    <p>
      你好，我是蘇里。这里是我的个人博客，用来记录工程实践、产品思考与个人成长。
    </p>
    <p>这是占位内容，欢迎随时替换为你的真实简介。</p>

    <h2>联系</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>邮箱：<a href="mailto:hello@yanguangjie.com">hello@yanguangjie.com</a></li>
      <li>GitHub：<a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@yanguangjie</a></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style is:global>
  .about .avatar {
    width: 112px;
    height: 112px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  .about h1 {
    font-size: 1.9rem;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .about h2 {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }
  .about p {
    margin: 1.25rem 0;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .about ul {
    padding-left: 1.4rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }
  .about a {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    text-decoration-color: var(--fg-subtle);
  }
</style>
